data.text:
Pre-recorded live from the upstate area, Vangelus and Seth Buzzard are joined by Krinsyn as a podcast is once again recorded in her home. Wear a friend as a fist and bro-bump your way into another set of Transformers talk!

00:00:00 - Opening

00:00:22 - Intro

00:02:13 - Transformers/JLA Crossover Concept

00:08:52 - New Pic Picks

00:23:19 - TFCCxEhobby

00:34:34 - Listener Question from CNCBrawl56

00:46:39 - Intermission

00:49:23 - What We Got This Week

00:57:14 - What High End Olive Oil We Got This Week

01:24:15 - Ending and Outro

Want to leave an audio listener question outside of Youtube or Private Messages? Call our WTF Hotline! These questions may be answered in recordings outside of numbered episodes, but feel free to mention your preference if it really matters to you.

That number is...

(318) 775-9830 or (318) 775-WTF0

Thank you so much! I need that shirt now!

Thanks for answering my questions guys and Krinsyn, I really enjoyed your reactions.

And you all really should come to Botcon 2013, because I plan to go, whether or not its in California, which will be a pretty crazy experience because I have never flown by myself before. So hopefully I can get a buddy to go with and cut class for a couple of days.

Yup awesome shirt. And mine is in the mail.

Whats the odds that shirt was for sale last week and all the Delorean talk on the podcast! Easily made that purchase that much more awesome.

OH and for those that don't know that shirt can never be bought again...(apparently you can but for significantly more money)! MY BAD

Ript appearal makes one shirt a day and you have 24 hours to buy it. If you don't order when you see it, you'll likely never see it again. I'm up to 5 shirts from them now including this one.

Wait, so I can't get that shirt? Hmm... how much more is significantly more...?
